Adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) zai karu cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashen Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Idan aka yi la'akari da cewa duk waɗanda suka kamu da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) za su nuna alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya a ƙasashen Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya, hakan zai tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa akwai dalilai daban-daban a kowace ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga abin da ya faru a Italiya, dole ne a shirya ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin gaggawa don karɓar yawancin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman a cikin gaggawa.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu mutane da dama da suka kamu da cutar numfashi da ba a san su ba a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa cutar ta samo asali ne daga sabon nau'in coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Daga nan, za a kira cutar da ta samo asali daga SARS-CoV-2 cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaidar da muke da ita a yau ta nuna cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da ke dauke da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, kamar rashin numfashi ko rashin numfashi, kuma yawancin za su warke.
Kashi 14 cikin 100 na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna fama da rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke bukatar a yi musu asibiti, kuma kashi 6 cikin 100 na mutanen da ke fama da cutar suna fama da rashin lafiya mai tsanani kuma suna bukatar a yi musu asibiti mai tsanani.
Yawan mutanen da aka kwantar da su asibiti saboda COVID-19 da suka mutu ya kai kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, za mu bincika sakamakon duk wani abu na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya (UK) kuma mu kwatanta shi da na lardin Hubei, China.
Za mu kuma kwatanta yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Birtaniya da na Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya
Kamar yadda a kasar Sin, COVID-19 ya bazu a wasu ƙasashe kuma cutar COVID-19 ta bazu a wasu ƙasashe kamar yadda ta faru a ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, darektan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A ranar 5 ga Maris, a cikin rahoton Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa, sun ba da labarin farkon mutanen Turai da suka kamu da COVID-19 bisa ga bayanin da WHO ta bayar.
A cikin kasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai, an fara samun mutum uku da suka kamu da cutar a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020; mutane ne da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China zuwa Faransa.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya (UK), kuma daga ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan kwanan wata, mutane 39,768 sun kamu da cutar da kuma mutane 1,727 sun mutu daga cutar da kuma a Italiya inda mutane 17,750 suka kamu da cutar amma mutane 1,441 sun mutu.
Samun cikakken adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa, wanda kawai ana samunsa daga kafofin na hukuma kamar ma'aikatar lafiya ta duniya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da kuma WHO, kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanin don gano yadda COVID-19 ke yaduwa a ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma Burtaniya, kuma ana kwatanta su da Italiya.
Game da yawan mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19, muna la'akari da kwanaki 14 na ƙarancin cutar COVID-19, don haka muna la'akari da ci gaban COVID-19, a kowace ƙasa ta Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya, a cikin lokacin daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma ba da cikakken adadin marasa lafiya a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da adadin Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Birtaniya
Matsakaicin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya ya biyo bayan na Hubei (China) (Lambar 1).
Ga kasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya, kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ta fara ƙaruwa a kusan ranar 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ta kai wani matsayi mai ƙarfi a kusan ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Ƙarin Bayani).
Wannan ya shafi yawan kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma a duk ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai, adadin kamuwa da COVID-19 ya karu daidai (Sauran Bayanai).
Lambar 2 za ta nuna jimlar adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19, a cikin ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
A ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na Turai da kuma Ƙasar Ingila sun sami adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar kamar Italiya, makonni uku ko makamancin haka.
Sakamakonmu zai nuna cewa yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 zai karu sosai a ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya.
Bayanai na kowa da kowa da ke da cutar COVID-19 za su nuna cewa cutar tana yaduwa a wasu ƙasashe.
Haka yake ko da yake ƙasashe suna da manufofi daban-daban, ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya ba sa ba da taimako iri ɗaya, kuma ƙila a wasu lokatai ana bayyana cutar a hanyoyi daban-daban a ƙasashe da kuma dokoki don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za su yi gwajin COVID-19, har ma da yin gwaji a baya.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitocin Italiya a wuraren da cutar ta kamu sun ce kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke dauke da COVID-19 suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ce kulawar gaggawa ta asibitoci a yankunan ta yi yawa.
Rahotanni na COVID-19 da aka yi asibiti da/ko kulawar gaggawa a yanzu suna cikin ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai na kashi 6% da 1% na yawan jama'a (ba a bayyana rahotanni ba).
Amma, ya kamata a haɗa su da kyau don a haɗa su da sabon bayani game da yawan waɗanda suka kamu da cuta da kuma mutuwar.
Wani bincike a 201011 ya nuna cewa an samu ci gaba sosai a cikin kulawar gaggawa da kuma matsakaiciyar gado a Turai, tare da gado 29.2 a Jamus da gado 4.2 a cikin mutane 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe suna iya samun damar yin aiki fiye da Italiya (12,5 a wuraren kula da marasa lafiya da matsakaicin gado ga mutane 100,000 a shekara ta 201011).
Inganta yanayin kula da marasa lafiya fiye da na likita, saboda kusan dukkanin kasashen Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya dangane da yawan mutanen da aka kwantar da su asibiti saboda COVID-19 da kuma saboda a &gt; 90% na haɗarin rashin bacci a cikin kulawa mai tsanani, an ba da su a cikin sabon tsarin ECDC na shida don nazarin gaggawa na COVID-19.
Domin yawan marasa lafiya a wasu yankunan Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Birtaniya, kuma ana amfani da asibitoci a wuraren kulawa mai tsanani don kula da mutane a wani yanki, dole ne a sami bayanai game da cututtuka da gadon kulawa mai tsanani a cikin wani ɓangare da ake kira Nomenclature na bayanai na matakin 2 (NUTS-2).
Labaran da aka samu a Italiya da kuma na yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya.
Dole ne ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani su shirya yadda za su magance karuwar kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma karuwar yawan mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 da ke neman taimako, musamman a cikin kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda za a yi a yankunan Italiya da cutar ta kamu.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken gaggawa na ECDC na kwanan nan, hanya mai sauri, mai inganci da inganci yana da mahimmanci don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, kawar da hankali daga kamuwa da cutar da kuma rage farashin contamintaion; saboda sanin yadda yawancin mutane ke kamuwa da cutar ba zai taimaka wa yanke shawara ba kuma asibitoci ba za su sami lokaci don fahimtar ta, yarda da ita da kuma shirya don taimako ba tare da an gwada ta ba.
Ana kuma tattauna tsarin kula da lafiyar mutane da yawa don a rage yaduwar cututtuka.
Akwai wata dama a lokacin da ƙasashe ke da damar da za su iya ƙara sarrafa ƙoƙarin da za a yi don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma matsa lamba a kan likitoci.
Idan ba a yi haka ba, cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai za su sami ƙarin marasa lafiya kuma za su bukaci a yi musu asibiti a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya samo asali ne daga cutar sankarar hanta ta SARS (SARS-CoV-2), ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta shafi mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya sanya ta zama babbar barazana ga rayuwar mutane.
A cikin dangantaka da ɗan'uwansa, SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da dubban mutane da cutar SARS a shekara ta 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya kasancewa daga beraye kuma yana da alamomi iri ɗaya da kuma kamuwa da cutar iri ɗaya.
Duk da haka, COVID-19 ba ta da tsanani sosai kuma ba ta da iyakacin cutar ta SARS amma tana da yawa kuma tana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma tana shafar maza fiye da mata.
Yayin da littattafai da ke magana game da wannan cuta za su ci gaba da yawaita, makasudin wannan talifin shi ne ya ba da bayanai a kan lokaci da kuma yin bayani game da bincike da za a yi a wannan batun.
Za mu tattauna muhimman bayanai game da cututtuka, yanayin rayuwa, ƙwayoyin cuta, yadda za a gano su, yadda za a warkar da su, yadda za a yi annobar, da kuma yadda za a hana su kamuwa da cutar.
Ko da yake ba a amsa tambayoyi da yawa ba, muna fata wannan talifin zai taimaka maka ka san yadda za ka magance wannan cuta mai tsanani.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga dukan 'yan kasar Sin, saboda an gaya musu kada su fita daga wurin a lokacin bikin da kuma makonni da suka gabata saboda sabon mummunan cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana da kamanceceniya da cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta kasance cutar ta numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a shekara ta 2003; kuma an sake kiranta SARS-CoV-2 a Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma ana kiran cutar da ta haifar da cutar COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Wannan cuta ta soma ne a birnin Wuhan da ke ƙasar Sin, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a dukan ƙasar Sin da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a faɗin duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta yi sanadiyar kamuwa da cutar COVID-19, fiye da mutane 40,000 sun warke kuma sun bar asibiti, fiye da mutane 3,000 sun mutu.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 ita ce "maƙiyi na farko na duniya" kuma zai iya zama mafi muni fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, mata sun wallafa labarai sama da 200 game da COVID-19 ciki har da cututtukan cututtuka, cututtuka, ilimin halayyar jiki, ganowa, da kuma maganin, tun lokacin da aka gabatar da rahoto na farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ke ba da cikakken bayani game da yadda cutar ta yadu.
Wannan talifin zai yi ƙoƙari ya taƙaita bincike da za a yi a kan wannan sabon yanayin da ke yaduwa cikin sauri.
Idan za ta yiwu, za mu gwada kwatancen COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wani cuta na CoV, cuta ta numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda aka saki a shekara ta 2012).
Za mu tattauna abin da muka koya game da yadda za mu magance wannan cuta da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci.
An ce CoVs ba su da sanadin mutuwa, musamman suna sa kashi 15 cikin 100 na mutane su yi sanyi 4.
Amma a wannan lokacin, mun sami ƙwayoyin cuta na CoVs masu cutarwa biyu, kamar su SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da cutar daga China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, kuma sun bazu cikin sauri zuwa wasu ƙasashe kuma sun sami kamuwa da cutar da yawa da kuma kashe mutane da yawa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine CoV na uku da ya faru a tarihin mutane.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin adadi. An fara bayar da rahoton cutar numfashi mai lamba 1,1, wanda ba a san asalinsa ba a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Fabrairu, 2019 a Hukumar Lafiya ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an gano yadda CoV ke farawa.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, mutum na farko ya mutu a Wuhan.
A lokacin, cutar ta yi yawa a birane da yankuna da kuma ƙasashe da ke kusa da birnin.
A ranar 20, an sanar da cewa an gano cutar, wanda ya nuna cewa za a iya canja wurin ta.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan kuma ba a samun isashen jiragen sama.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairu, an fara binciken cutar, daga cikin mutane 41 da suka kamu da cutar, mutane 21 ne kawai suka isa kasuwar kifi ta Wuhan inda cutar ta fito ne daga wani dabba da ba a san inda ta fito ba.
A ranar 30 ga Janairu, Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana cewa cutar tana da haɗari a duniya.
A lokacin da aka rubuta wannan rahoton, cutar ta riga ta bazu a dukan ƙasar Sin da kuma wasu ƙasashe kusan 50 a duniya (Lambar 2.2).
Da yake yanayin zai canja a nan gaba, ba a san yadda za a yi amfani da shi ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken da aka yi wa marasa lafiya 8,866 da kuma mutane 4,021 da ke dauke da cutar COVID-19 ya nuna sabon bayani game da cutar a matsayin ƙasa (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 zai iya kamuwa da mutane na kowane zamani, amma galibi tsakanin shekaru 30 zuwa 65.
Kusan kashi 47.7 cikin ɗari na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun fi shekara 50 girma, kuma kaɗan ne daga cikinsu ba su kai shekara 20 ba, kuma 14 ne kawai suka kamu da cutar ba su kai shekara 10.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi yawan kamuwa da maza (0,31/100,000) fiye da mata (0,27/100,000).
COVID-19 ya bazu cikin ƙungiyoyi musamman a Hubei da kewaye da shi.
COVID-19 ya ɗauki matsakaici kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga lokacin da aka fara zuwa ranar da aka gano shi.
Matsakaicin kwanaki kafin bayyanar cutar ya kai kwanaki 4.8 (3,0-7,2).
Matsakaicin kwanaki daga haihuwar mutum zuwa mutuwa kwanaki 9.5 ne (4,8-13).
Yawan haifuwa (R0) ya kai 3.77 (95% CI: 3,51-4,05), kuma canjin R0 ya kai 2.23-4.82.
Yawan kamuwa da cutar ya karu da yawa kafin 23 ga Janairu, 2020, daidai da lokacin da aka yi amfani da kayan aiki a bikin bazara na kasar Sin.
Yawan mutuwar da aka samu a cikin marasa lafiya ya kai kashi 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), kuma yawan mutuwar da aka samu ya kai kashi 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Abubuwa uku da suka fi sa mutum cikin haɗari da cutar COVID-19 sune jima'i (maza), shekaru (≥60) da kuma numfashi mai tsanani.
