A cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an yi amfani da shi a dukan ƙasar Sin da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a faɗin duniya a lokacin da muke rubuta wannan labarin.
Saboda wannan kwayar cutar tana da kamanceceniya da SARS-CoV kuma alamun cutar suna kama da COVID-19 da SARS, barkewar COVID-19 ta haifar da wani abu na SARS.
Amma akwai bambanci mai muhimmanci tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, wanda ke da muhimmanci wajen hana cutar da kuma warkar da masu kamuwa da ita.
COVID-19 ya fi rinjayar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, kuma ya fi rinjayar tsofaffi fiye da mata.
SARS zai kashe mutane fiye da COVID-19 (10,91% da 1,44%).
Mutane da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 sun kamu da cutar ko da ba su da wata alama amma mutanen da ke fama da cutar SARS suna kamuwa da cutar ne kawai idan sun kamu da cutar sosai, saboda haka yana da wuyar hana COVID-19 yadawa fiye da SARS.
Wannan zai bayyana dalilin da ya sa SARS-CoV-2 ya fi yawa kuma ya fi yawa fiye da SARS-CoV.
Idan muka yi gwajin RNA na SARS-CoV-2 na yau da kullum, babu wataƙila wasu mutane da suka kamu da COVID-19 da za su iya kamuwa da cutar.
Amma, waɗanda suka tsira za su iya samun cutar.
Wannan ya ƙara haɗarin yaduwar ƙwayoyin cuta.
Don ci gaban bincike na COVID-19 ya yi sauri, akwai wasu muhimman abubuwan da za a inganta, kamar:
Daga ina SARS-CoV-2 ya fito?
Ko da yake akwai kusan kashi 96% na irin wannan yanayin tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da kuma SARS CoVs guda biyu da suka fito daga beraye, ba za a iya tabbatar da cewa SARS-CoV-2 ya fito ne daga beraye ba.
Waɗanne dabbobi ne suka sami kwayar cutar bayan sun bar wurin zama, wato, ƙwari, har zuwa mutane?
Idan ba mu san amsoshin tambaya na 1 da 2 ba, ba za mu iya hana su yin yaduwa ba, kuma za su iya sake faruwa a kowane lokaci.
Ko da yake nazarin kwayoyin halitta da kuma nazarin halittu sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da alaƙa da ACE2, shin ba mu san yadda kwayar cutar take shiga cikin ƙwayoyin huhu ba kuma tana haifar da canji?
Shin ƙwayoyin cuta suna da alaƙa da ACE2- a wasu kwayoyin halitta?
Idan ba mu san amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin ba, ba za mu iya sanin magani da zai iya magance su ba.
Har yaushe za a ci gaba da wannan cuta?
Ta yaya ƙwayoyin cuta suke shiga cikin jini?
Shin zai zama annoba ta duniya, ko kuwa zai ƙare kamar SARS ko kuma zai zama annoba ta yau da kullum kamar mura?
Yana da muhimmanci amma yana iya ɗaukan lokaci kafin a sami amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da ke sama da kuma wasu tambayoyi da yawa.
Amma, ko da mene ne zai iya jawo mana hasara, abin da za mu yi shi ne mu kawar da cututtuka da wuri-wuri kuma mu dawo da rayuwarmu.
Kwayar cutar korona ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi
Canjin da ake samu a cikin kwayoyin halitta yana sa kwayar cutar korona (CoVs) ta ci gaba da bunkasa da kuma adanawa, ciki har da mutane, tsawon shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an gano cewa CoVs (HCoVs) biyu na mutum ba sa haifar da cututtuka masu tsanani, kamar sanyi.
Cutar huhu mai tsanani (SARS) da kuma cutar ta numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun nuna yadda cutar HCoV ke iya cutar da mutane da kuma kashe su.
Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar kasar Sin a ƙarshen 2019 ta sanya CoVs a saman matsayi kuma ta ba mu mamaki yadda suke yaduwa cikin sauri amma suna da ƙananan haɗari fiye da ɗan'uwan su SARS-CoV.
HCoVs na iya kamuwa da cutar daga dabbobi kuma gano dabbobi da suka haifar da HCoVs zai taimaka mana mu ma.
Yawancin HCoVs sun fito ne daga beraye amma ba su haifar da cututtuka ba.
An kuma san wasu abubuwan da ke tsakanin HCoVs.
Sanin dabbobi masu dauke da cutar yana da muhimmanci wajen magance cututtukan da ke faruwa a mutane.
Ƙari ga haka, bincike game da dangantaka tsakanin dabbobi da ke kaiwa ga cutar CoV zai iya taimaka wajen gano cutar a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan labarin, za mu taƙaita abin da muka sani game da HCoVs bakwai, kuma mu mai da hankali ga tarihin gano su da kuma yadda suka samo asali daga dabbobi da kuma abubuwan da ke taimakawa wajen yada su.
Abu mai mahimmanci shi ne cewa muna kwatanta da rarrabe yawancin HCoVs bisa ga ci gaban kwayar cutar da kuma yadda kwayoyin halitta ke haɗuwa.
An tattauna cutar COVID-19 ta yanzu ta 2019 a wannan talifin.
Ƙari ga haka, ya tattauna bukatar da ake yi don a magance matsalolin da ke jawo cututtuka da kuma sakamakon ci gaban ƙwayoyin cuta.
Kwayoyin cutar Coronaviruses (CoVs) suna cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ke cikin rukuni na ƙwayoyin RNA masu ƙarfi.
Kwayar cuta mai girma daga 26 zuwa 32 kilobases a cikin RNAs an kira su CoVs saboda suna da kambi a cikin microscope na lantarki.
A jikinta, CoVs ba su da tsarin kwayoyin halitta da suka yi daidai.
Kusan kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta suna da sassan biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), wanda aka fassara tsakanin pp1 da pp1ab a cikin furotin.
Ana kuma amfani da wasu sunadarai don samar da sunadarai 16 da ba su da ƙarfi, wato, nsp1~16.
Sauran kwayoyin halitta suna da ORFs don gina jiki, ciki har da ƙwayoyin cuta (S), fata (E), membrane (M) da nucleoproteins (N).
Wasu sunadarai na musamman suna da lambobin da ke cikin jerin CoVs.
Bisa ga bambancin tsarin sunadarai, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa manyan nau'ikan hudu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), kuma beta-CoV yana da yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarraba su zuwa nau'ikan hudu (A, B, C da D).
Shaidar kwayoyin halitta ta nuna cewa beraye da beraye sune tushen asalin kwayoyin halitta na yawancin ƙwayoyin alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, amma tsuntsaye sune tushen tushen tushen gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sukan haɗu a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta kuma wasu sun zama ƙwayoyin cuta masu tsanani na ɗan adam.
Har zuwa yau, an gano nau'ikan cutar CoV guda bakwai na mutum (HCoVs).
Daga cikin su HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
Kusan nau'ikan beta-CoV guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, cutar sankarar hanta ta coronavirus (SARS-CoV), cutar sankarar hanta ta coronavirus ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da kuma SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna da alamun bayyanar cututtuka masu sauƙi, kamar sanyi da/ko kumburi.
Sabbin cututtukan SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 sun bambanta, suna da matukar tasiri, suna hana yawan mutanen da ke fama da cutar ta numfashi da ke haifar da tashin hankali (ARDS) da sauran cututtukan huhu.
An gano alamar farko ta HCoV-229E, B814, daga kwayoyin hanci na marasa lafiya masu sanyi a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, bincike ya ci gaba da taimakawa wajen gano HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, dukansu ba su da alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
Hakika, mutane da yawa sun amince da ra'ayin cewa cutar HCoVs ba ta da tasiri har zuwa lokacin da SARS ta fara.
Cutar SARS ta 2003 ta kasance ɗaya daga cikin cututtukan cututtukan zamani mafi tsanani, ta shafi mutane fiye da 8,000 kuma kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 sun mutu.
Bayan shekaru goma, cutar ta numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta zama babbar cuta a yankin Larabawa kuma ta bazu ko'ina cikin duniya.
Sabuwar cutar HCoV (2019-nCoV) ta 2019, wanda aka sake sanyawa SARS-CoV-2, ita ce tushen cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta riga ta kashe mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ta sami kamuwa da mutane sama da 91,000 har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi gargadi kuma duniya tana shirin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Dukkanin HCoVs bakwai sun fito ne daga dabbobi, wato beraye, beraye, ko wasu dabbobi.
Akwai hujjoji da yawa da za su nuna cewa dukkanin HCoVs sun fito ne daga beraye, inda ƙwayoyin cuta suke zama da sauƙi amma suna da nau'i-nau'i masu yawa.
Cutar COVID-19 ta zama babbar matsala ga likitoci, masana kimiyya, al'adu da al'adun jama'ar Sin da na duniya.
Kula da dabbobi a inda HCoVs ke fitowa yana taimakawa wajen gano tarihin halitta, ikon sarrafawa da abubuwan da ke hana halittu masu tashi.
Hakanan zai iya jagorantar ko taimakawa wajen gano wuri, hanyar wucewa da kuma shirya kwayoyin halitta da ke hana cutar SARS-CoV-2, da kuma ƙoƙarin hana ta yaduwa a nan gaba.
A cikin wannan labarin, za mu tattauna yadda wadannan dabbobi suka fito, yadda ake watsa su zuwa wasu kwayoyin halitta da kuma yadda ake kamuwa da cutar HCoVs.
Musamman, muna magana ne game da wani abu mai mahimmanci cewa manyan ƙwayoyin cuta na HCoVs ba sa kamuwa da cutar a cikin yanayin da suke zaune amma suna kamuwa da cutar idan sun fito daga wani halittar kuma sun shiga cikin sabon yanayi.
An kuma tattauna yadda HCoV ke tasowa da kuma yadda yawanci ana watsa shi zuwa wasu halittu ke rage yawan kamuwa da cutar.
An kuma tattauna sakamakon cutar SARS-CoV-2 a wannan labarin.
An san dabbobi masu cutar ta CoV tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
Kafin a gano alamar farko ta HCoV-229E, B814, a cikin hancin marasa lafiya masu sanyi, an riga an gano CoVs a cikin dabbobi da yawa, kamar su dindon, beraye, shanu, aladu, kuliyoyi da karnuka.
A cikin shekaru da suka gabata, an gano nau'ikan HCoV guda bakwai.
Wannan taƙaitaccen bayanin gano HCoV a cikin jerin abubuwan da aka yi (Table 1) zai zama mai amfani kuma zai koya mana abubuwa da yawa.
An gano alamar farko ta HCoV-229E ta hanyar numfashi a cikin mutanen da ke fama da cutar ta hanyar numfashi a shekara ta 1966, kuma daga baya ta ci gaba zuwa kwayoyin cuta na WI-38.
Mutane da ke dauke da cutar HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun sanyi da zafi, ciwon hanci, ciwon hanci da kuma jin zafi da zazzabi da kuma tari sun bayyana a kashi 10~20 cikin dari na mutane.
Daga baya a shekara ta 1967, HCoV-OC43 ya fito daga cikin kwayoyin halitta kuma ya wuce cikin kwakwalwar da aka samu a cikin berayen da suka mamaye ƙasa.
Alamomin cutar HCoV-OC43 sun yi kama da HCoV-229E, wanda ya yi kama da cututtukan da ke haifar da cutar numfashi, kamar su ƙwayoyin cuta na A da rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 sun bazu a duniya, kuma ana ba da su ne a lokacin sanyi.
Sau da yawa, ana haifan ƙwayoyin cuta biyu a cikin mako guda, bayan haka ana kamuwa da su a cikin kusan mako biyu.
Bisa ga binciken da aka yi na kyauta na mutum, mutane masu lafiya da suka kamu da cutar HCoV-229E suna fuskantar sanyi sau da yawa.
Mutane da yawa da suka kamu da rashin ƙarfi ne kawai suka kamu da rashin numfashi.
SARS, wanda kuma ake kira rush disease, shi ne HCoV na farko da ya haifar da annobar cutar a tarihin ɗan adam kuma ya samo asali ne daga SARS-CoV, HCoV na uku da aka gano.
Wataƙila mutum na farko da ya kamu da cutar SARS ya faru ne a shekara ta 2002 a lardin Guangdong, a ƙasar Sin.
Cutar SARS ta yi sanadiyar kamuwa da mutane 8,096 da mutuwar mutane 774, kuma ta bazu a ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da dama.
Ban da kayan da ke cikinta, an gano cewa duk wanda ya karɓi ita zai iya ba da ita ga mutane kusan na biyu - kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 kafin ta bayyana kuma ta zama mai ƙarfi a rana ta goma bayan an karɓe ta.
Mutane da suka kamu da SARS-CoV suna da ciwon jijiyoyin jiki, zafi, zazzabi, kumburi, da sanyi, sannan kuma suna jin rashin numfashi, numfashi da kuma numfashi.
Ragewar ƙwayar lymphocyte, lalacewar aikin jini, da kuma karuwar creatine kinase na cikin cututtukan SARS.
Rashin alveolar, saurin fitowar kwayoyin epithelial da kuma karuwa a cikin macrophages na iya faruwa a cikin masu cutar SARS.
Kimanin kashi 20 zuwa 30 cikin 100 na waɗanda suka kamu da cutar za su shiga asibiti kuma za su bukaci taimako na iska.
Bugu da ƙari, a cikin numfashi, gabobin jiki da yawa kamar su ƙwayar cuta, ƙuƙwalwa da koda suna iya lalacewa idan cutar ta yi tsanani, kuma hakan yakan haifar da yawan kwayoyin cytokines, wanda zai iya zama sanadiyyar mutuwar marasa lafiya.
An fara gano cutar ne a gwajin naman naman ɗan'uwan wani mai cutar da ya ƙaura daga birnin Guangzhou zuwa Hong Kong.
Tun daga lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai wajen gudanar da bincike kan HCoV.
An gano HCoV-NL63 a cikin jariri mai wata bakwai a ƙasar Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
A dā, ana ganin cewa ana yawan cutar a cikin matasa da tsofaffi da kuma waɗanda suke da rashin lafiya da kuma rashin numfashi.
Alamomin hanci, haɗuwa, zazzabi, da cututtukan numfashi sun fi yawa a cikin cutar HCoV-NL63.
Wani bincike ya nuna cewa an samo wani kwayar cutar daga hanci na wani yaro mai wata takwas da ke fama da ciwon huhu a ƙasar Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a ƙasar Netherlands, amma ya bazu a ko'ina.
An kiyasta cewa cutar HCoV-NL63 tana haifar da kusan kashi 4.7% na kamuwa da cutar numfashi, kuma yawancin mutane sun kamu da cutar a farkon bazara, bazara, da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana haifar da cututtukan numfashi na laryngitis, wanda ake kira croup.
A wannan shekarar, an gano HCoV-HKU1 a cikin wani mutum mai shekaru 71 da aka kwantar da shi asibiti saboda cutar huhu da bronchiolitis a Hong Kong.
Baya ga cututtukan huhu da bronchiolitis, HCoV-HKU1 ya kasance yana da alaƙa da cutar asma mai tsanani.
Kamar yadda yake a cikin HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, an gano HCoV-HKU1 a duniya, kuma hakan ya haifar da cututtukan numfashi.
Dukkanin HCoVs guda huɗu suna da kyau ga mutane kuma galibi suna da ƙarancin haɗari saboda rashin ƙarfi, koda kuwa haɗarin ya faru ne saboda dalilai da ba a sani ba kuma tare da alamun ƙarancin haɗari na HCoV-NL63 mai ƙarfi, wanda kwanan nan aka ce zai haifar da ƙananan cututtukan numfashi a China.
Sau da yawa, yayin da HCoVs da za a iya watsa su cikin mutane da kyau kuma su kasance a cikin jikin mutum, ba su da ƙarfi sosai ko kuma ba su da lafiya sosai.
An fara gano cutar MERS-CoV a shekarar 2012 a cikin wani mutum mai shekaru 60 da haihuwa wanda ke fama da ciwon huhu da kuma lalacewar koda a Saudiyya.
Ko da yake yawancin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an yi amfani da su wajen yaɗa cutar saboda yawanci suna da haɗuwa da mutane a ƙasashen Turai da Tunisiya.
Wani ƙaramin tashin hankali da aka yi a Koriya ta Kudu a shekara ta 2015 ya kai mutane 186.
Alamomin MERS suna kama da na SARS, ana iya ganin su a cikin cututtukan huhu masu tsanani.
Ba kamar SARS ba, yawancin mutanen da ke fama da cutar MERS sun kamu da cutar koda mai tsanani, wadda ba ta dace da cutar MERS a cikin sauran cututtukan HCoV ba.
Mutane fiye da 30 sun nuna alamun cututtukan da ke tattare da cututtukan jijiyoyin jiki, kamar su kumburi da tari.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an kiyasta cewa akwai mutane sama da 2,500 da suka kamu da cutar kuma an kashe kashi 34.4 cikin ɗari, wanda ya sa cutar ta MERS-CoV ta zama ɗaya daga cikin cututtukan da suka fi kashe mutane.
A ƙarshen Disamba 2019, an gano mutane da ke fama da cutar numfashi da aka riga aka sani da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana cutar ta hanyar numfashi da ta samo asali daga SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya na duniya kuma ta sanya sunan COVID-19.
A ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020, an samu kamuwa da cutar a duniya ta mutum 90,053, kuma adadin mutuwar ya kai kashi 3.4%.
Abin lura, adadin mutuwar a birnin Hubei na kasar Sin ya kai kashi 4.2 cikin dari, amma a wajen ya kai kashi 1.2 cikin dari.
SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da cututtukan numfashi masu tsanani kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV; ana nuna su ta hanyar zazzabi, tari da kuma wahalar numfashi.
Wasu kuma suna fama da ciwon kumburi.
Cutar huhu na iya zama wata alama mai tsanani kuma tana iya zama ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Ko da yake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da kamanceceniya sosai don samar da kashi 82% na nucleotides, an rarraba su zuwa nau'ikan cututtuka.
SARS-CoV-2 ba shi da ƙarfi sosai amma yana da yawa idan aka gano shi a cikin kusanci da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An kuma gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin mutanen da ba su da alamun cutar kuma wataƙila hakan ya sa ta bazu cikin sauri a duniya.
A cikin kwatancen da aka yi na SARS-CoV-2 da HCoVs shida, akwai wasu kamanceceniya da bambance-bambance masu ban sha'awa.
Na farko, lokaci da kuma tsawon lokacin da za a kamu da cutar suna da alaƙa sosai.
A wannan yanayin, SARS-CoV-2 yana da daidaituwa da manyan cututtuka na HCoVs shida.
Na biyu, an gano cewa cutar ta COVID-19 tana da matukar tasiri a tsakanin SARS-CoV da sauran HCoVs hudu (misali, HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63).
A wani ɓangare, cutar SARS-CoV-2 tana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka na yau da kullun a cikin cutar HCoVs da aka gano a cikin mutane, har ma da bayyanar cututtuka marasa kyau, marasa kyau, ko ma babu alamun bayyanar.
A wasu lokuta, mutane kalilan da ke da cutar COVID-19 mai tsanani za su iya kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV, ko da kuwa adadin ya rage.
Na uku, watsa SARS-CoV-2 ya nuna irin wannan hali ga HCoVs na mutum da SARS-CoV.
Bugu da ƙari, kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ya fi na HCoVs na mutum girma.
A wani ɓangare kuma, ana buƙatar sake duba ko kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 tana raguwa bayan kamuwa da cutar kamar yadda SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV suka yi.
A ƙarshe, kamar sauran HCoVs, SARS-CoV-2 na iya faruwa a cikin haushi.
Ko da yake SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da cutar a cikin fitsari yana da mahimmanci kamar yadda ya faru don SARS-CoV, ana buƙatar ƙarin bincike don bayyana shi a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Yana da ban sha'awa sosai a gano ko SARS-CoV-2 na iya faruwa a cikin yanayi kamar yadda yake faruwa a cikin HCoVs na mutum.
Duk da haka, wasu nau'ikan SARS-CoV-2 da kuma yadda ake watsa su, yadda suke bayyana da kuma yadda suke yaduwa bayan sun shiga cikin mutum zai iya shafar yaduwar COVID-19.
Dukkanin HCoVs na mutum suna haifar da ƙananan alamun da suka saba da jikin mutum.
A wasu hanyoyi, yana iya zama gaskiya cewa mata sun saba da HCoVs huɗu.
A wasu kalmomin, duka biyu na iya zama masu cutar HCoV da suka riga sun warke.
HCoVs da suka haifar da cututtuka masu tsanani da kuma mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HCoV sun cire cutar.
Don su yi aiki, dole ne a haifi HCoVs a cikin cikakkun kwayoyin halitta don sababbin su fito don magance matsalolin da ke cikin gida.
Saboda haka, idan SARS-CoV-2 ya daɗe kuma mutane da yawa sun kamu da cutar, chances na kamuwa da cutar sun fi girma.
Idan aka yi amfani da shi sosai, zai fi wuya mutane su hana shi kamuwa da cututtuka ta hanyar yin amfani da takunkumi ko kuma wasu hanyoyin da za su iya kaiwa ga cututtuka.
A cikin shekaru da yawa, CoVs huɗu masu kamuwa da cuta suna yawo a cikin mutane, suna ba da sanyi ga waɗanda suka kamu da cutar.
Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta ba sa bukatar su ɓoye a cikin dabbobi.
A akasin haka, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV masu cutarwa ba su da daidaito a jikin mutum kuma ba su da daidaito a hana yaduwar su cikin mutane.
Za su yi rayuwa a cikin dabbobi kuma su yi amfani da wata hanya mai kyau don su kai su wurin mutane.
SARS-CoV-2 yana da alamun bayyanar cututtuka kamar SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV da kuma HCoVs huɗu da aka kamu da su.
Yana da matukar yaduwa kamar HCoVs na mutum, koda kuwa a yanzu.
Amma, yana da tasiri sosai fiye da HCoVs na mutum amma ba shi da tasiri kamar SARS-CoV ko MERS-CoV.
Za mu jira mu ga ko zai iya zama mutum kuma ya yi tafiya a tsakanin mutane ba tare da wata hanya ko dabba ba.
Kafin mu tattauna asalin HCoVs, zai dace mu tattauna ma'anar su da kuma yadda suke girma, halitta, yanayin rayuwa, wurare da kuma abubuwan da ke sa HCoVs su kasance da ƙarfi.
Hanyar HCoV tana girma ne a cikin dabba idan ta kasance a cikin ƙwayar da ke da haɗari mai ƙarfi ga haɓakar nucleotides.
Wannan ƙwayar cuta tana da ƙarfi sosai kuma ba ta da lahani.
Hakazalika, wani abu da ke dauke da HCoV yana iya yin amfani da shi a cikin dogon lokaci.
