A shekara ta 2008, an gudanar da wani bincike a Jami'ar Westminster da ke London, wanda aka tallafa wa kamfanin samar da kayan shafawa na Turai, don a fahimci bambancin da ke tsakanin kayan shafawa, na'urar shafawa da kuma sabon na'urar shafawa.
Bayan an wanke hannuwanmu kuma an bushe su da na'urar bushewa, adadin ƙwayoyin cuta a yatsunsu ya ƙaru da kashi 194% kuma a hannayenmu ya ƙaru da kashi 254%.
