A cikin nazarin asibitoci na rashin lafiyar staphylococcus, an lura cewa amfanin wanke hannu ya fi yawa bayan kashi 20 cikin 100 na farko, kuma amfanin da aka samu a wanke hannu ya fi yawa har kashi 35 cikin 100.
