Ranar wanke hannu ga jama'a misali ne na wani taron firist da ke taimakawa wajen sauya halaye. Yayin da cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20 ta barke, UNICEF ta ƙarfafa samar da wani motsin rai na wanke hannu.
