Angiotensin yana rubuta enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne da ke waje da ƙwayar cuta, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda da jijiyoyin jiki.
ACE2 yana hana angiotensin zuwa enzyme (ACE) ta hanyar rage yawan angiotensin-II da kuma inganta ang(1-7) don yin amfani da shi a maganin cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma ana amfani da shi don kamuwa da cutar coronavirus.
A jikin mutum, ana kiran wannan enzyme hACE2.
Angiotensin encoded enzyme 2 wani enzyme ne mai dauke da zinx a jikin endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Protein ACE2 yana dauke da N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma C-terminal na hanci na ammonium acid.
ACE2 yana samar da nau'in membrane na furotin guda ɗaya, yana aiki ne na ƙirar enzyme a waje da ƙwayoyin halitta da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Ƙarin ƙwayoyin halitta na ACE2 suna samo asali ne daga wani enzyme mai suna sheddase, wanda ke sa furotin ya shiga jini kuma ya fito daga cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin kwayoyin halitta da yawa: ACE2 yana da alaƙa da membrane na ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na nau'in II na ƙwayoyin alveolarenterocytes na ƙwayoyin cuta, jijiyoyi da jijiyoyin endothelial da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta masu sauƙi a cikin kwayoyin halitta.
Ƙari ga haka, ACE2 mRNA yana cikin ƙwayar cuta, striatum, ypothalamus, da kuma ƙwayar kwakwalwa.
Aikin farko na aCE2 shi ne aikin ACE.
ACE yana ɗaure hormone na angiotensin I zuwa vasoconstriction na angiotensin II.
ACE2 yana haɗuwa da carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine zuwa angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-pPhe) kuma yana haɗuwa da shi a cikin vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma yana iya ɗaurewa da wasu ƙwayoyin cuta irin su [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita ƙwayoyin cuta na amino acid na tsaka tsaki wanda ke ɗauke da SLC6A19 kuma yana da cututtukan Hartnup.
Bincika furotin na transmembrane, ACE2 shine farkon hanyar shigarwar kwayar cutar coronavirus, da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus da SARS ya samo asali); da kuma SARS-CoV-2 (virus da COVID-19 ya samo asali).
A cikin fahimtar da ta dace, haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na SARS-CoV1 da SARS-CoV2 da enzyme ACE2 a saman ƙwayoyin halitta zai haifar da endocytosis da kuma sarrafa kwayar cutar ta enzyme tare da ɗayan endosomes na ƙwayoyin halitta.
Wannan cibiyar ta shiga ta samar da furotin S da kuma protease serine TMPRSS2, wanda ke gano magani mai amfani wanda ya sa wasu mutane su kwafa ACE2, a cikin kwayoyin halitta, don gwadawa don yaki da kamuwa da cuta.
Amma, ƙananan jami'an ilimi da kuma hukumomi sun ce ya kamata a ci gaba da amfani da ACE da kuma maganin ARB.
Wani bincike na tsarin da kuma nazarin meta da aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012 ya gano cewa ta amfani da ACE zai rage yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar huhu da kashi 34%.
Amma, haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu ya ragu a cikin waɗanda aka yi wa maganin ACE waɗanda suka samu damar kamuwa da cutar saurin, musamman waɗanda suka kamu da cututtukan zuciya.
Ana kuma haɗa maganin ACE don rage cutar huhu don hana mutuwa, amma sakamakon bai kasance mai tsanani ba ga haɗarin cutar huhu.
Maganin da ake kira ACE2 na mutum (rhACE2) sabon magani ne na ciwon huhu, kuma yana taimakawa wajen cutar haemodynacy da oxygenation a cikin aladu da lypopolysaccharia a cikin cutar rashin numfashi.
Rayuwar rhACE2 a cikin mutane na tsawon sa'o'i 10 kuma zai yi aiki na minti 30 a cikin sa'o'i 24.
