Dabara ta biyu, allurar rigakafi ta subunit, za ta yi ƙoƙarin samar da allurar rigakafi da za ta sa tsarin rigakafi ya zama mai ƙwarewa ga ainihin allurar rigakafi na kwayar.
A cikin SARS-CoV-2, wannan binciken ya mayar da hankali ne ga furotin na spicule-S wanda ke taimakawa kwayar cutar ta shiga cikin mai karɓar enzyme ACE2.
Hanyar na uku ita ce yin allurar nucleic acid (DNA ko RNA, sabuwar fasaha don inganta allurar rigakafi).
Ana buƙatar gwajin allurar rigakafi ta amfani da waɗannan dabarun don tabbatar da tsaro da kuma amfani da su. A ranar 16 ga Maris, 2020, an fara gasar farko ta allurar rigakafi a asibiti tare da masu son shiga hudu a Seattle.
An yi amfani da allurar rigakafi da ba ta da lambar kwafin kwayoyin halitta na cutar daga kwayar cutar da ke haifar da cutar. An yi tunanin cewa karuwar ƙarfin wannan maganin rigakafi a wurin yaƙi zai iya zama ci gaban allurar SARS-COV-2, amma har yanzu batun jayayya ne.
An gudanar da gwaje-gwaje na asibiti sama da 300 a watan Afrilu 2020.
Gwaje-gwaje bakwai suna nazarin hanyoyin da aka amince da su don magance cutar zazzabin cizon sauro, kuma hudu na yanzu suna nazarin hydroxychloroquine ko chloroquine.
An shirya maganin rigakafi don wani dalili da ya sa aka yi amfani da shi a duk binciken da aka yi a kasar Sin, tare da gwaje-gwaje na III na tara na rigakafin remdesivir da za a yi a ƙasashe da yawa da za a bayar da rahoto a ƙarshen Afrilu.
Ana iya amincewa da nazarin nazarin halittu na ci gaban asibiti na allurar rigakafin COVID-19 a watan Afrilu 2020. Ana nazarin ƙarin alluran rigakafin riga-kafi da yawa don maganin COVID-19, kamar remdesivir, chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir da lopinavir/ritonavir tare da interferon beta.
Alamar ta fara bayyana ne a sakamakon cutar remdesivir, a watan Maris na shekarar 2020.
An samu ci gaba a asibiti a cikin marasa lafiya da aka yi amfani da remdesivir a maganin zubar da jini.
Ana gudanar da gwaje-gwaje na asibiti na Phase III a cikin EU, China da Italiya. Chloroquine, wanda aka fara amfani da shi don magance zazzabin cizon sauro, an yi nazari a kasar Sin a watan Fabrairu na shekarar 2020, a farkon kamuwa da cutar.
